# Product Carbon Footprint Analyzer — v1 Spec

## What this tool does

The tool estimates product carbon footprint(PCF) using product's bill of material data which can be messy. The input is the Bill of Materials, and the output is the total carbon footprint of the product as well breakdown of emission for the product at component level. The tool either flags or fixes the incomplete or anomalous data in the bill of material, matches the emission factor or flags the mismatch and calculates emission based on the BOM and emission factor data.

## Input Schema

| Column | Type | Required | Description |
|--------|------|----------|-------------|
| component | string | yes | the name of the component |
| material | string | yes | the material used in the component |
| quantity | float | yes | quantity of components |
| spend_usd | float | yes | weight of the material in kilogram(kg)|
| weight_kg | float | no | weight of the material in kilogram(kg)|
| supplier | string | no | supplier of the component |
| country_of_origin | string | no | Country of origin of the material |

File must be CSV format, UTF-8 encoded, 
maximum 500 rows and 5MB.


## Output Schema

### Summary
| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| product_name | string | Name of the product |
| total_kg_co2e | float | Total footprint |
| matched_items | int | BOM rows successfully matched |
| flagged_items | int | BOM rows flagged for review |


### Line Item Breakdown
| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| component | string | From input BOM |
| material | string | From input BOM |
| weight_kg | float | Normalized weight |
| emission_factor | float | Matched EF value |
| ef_unit | string | Unit of the EF |
| ef_source | string | Database source |
| kg_co2e | float | Calculated footprint |
| share_pct | float | % of total footprint |

on-screen table and downloadable CSV

