### Example 3: Reusable water bottle (edge case)


| component | material | quantity | spend_usd | weight_kg | supplier | country_of_origin |
| --------- | -------- | -------- | ---- | --------- | -------- | ----------------- |
| body | stainless steel | 1 | 10 | 0.3 | ABCD | India |
| Lid | SS304 | 1 | 3 | 0.07 | abc | India |
| Gasket/Seal | Silicone | 1 | 1 | 0.0008 | cvb | India |
| Insulation | aerogel | 1 | 2 | 0.0001 | dfgh | India |
| Antimicrobial treatment | tritan copolyester | 1 | 2 | 0.0001 | bnm | India |
| packaging | cardboard | 1 | 1 | 0.050 | ert | china |
| packaging | coating | 1 | 1 | 0.005 | ert | china |

Expected behavior: 
- Rows 1 and 2: tool recognizes "stainless steel" 
  and "SS304" as potential duplicates, flags for review
- Row 4: "aerogel" has no match in factor database, 
  flags for human input
- Row 5: "Tritan copolyester" has no match, 
  flags for human input  
- Row 7: "coating" is ambiguous, suggest nearest 
  matches (powder coat, paint, anodizing), flag

## Failure Modes

| Failure | Trigger | Tool behavior |
|---------|---------|---------------|
| Unreadable file | corrupted CSV, wrong format | Show an error "unreadable file" and ask user to upload a valid file |
| Empty BOM | file uploads but has no data rows | Show an error "empty file" and ask user to upload a non empty file |
| No matched factors | none of the materials match | Don't show total footprint. show the lineitem breakdown table showing parsed BOM and flags |
| Partial match | some rows match, some don't | show total footprint with a completeness warning, show breakdown table with matched and flagged rows clearly distinguished. |
| All flagged | every row has issues | Don't show total footprint. show the lineitem breakdown table showing parsed BOM and flags |
| Column missing | required column is missing | Show an error "missing column" and ask user to upload a valid file with all the columns |
| Large file | more than 500 rows | Show an error to use that tool only supports 500 rows |

